{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~kobsa/courses/ICS104/course-notes/game-design.htm", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd\">\n<html><head>\n<meta content=\"text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1\" http-equiv=\"content-type\"><title>Game design</title></head><body><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\" size=\"+3\"><big><big><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Game design</span></big></big><br>\n<br>\nT<span style=\"font-style: italic;\">ypes of games:<br>\n</span>action, shooter, adventure, role-playing, simulation, strategy, single vs. (massive) multi-player, etc.</font><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\" size=\"+3\"><br>\n<br>\nTypical\ngoals in \"general HCI design\": <br>\nreduce error rate, increase speed of\ntask performance, improve retention, user satisfaction...</font><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\" size=\"+3\"><br>\n<br>\nAdditional predominant goal in game design: give users \"<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">fun</span>\"</font><br>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><font size=\"+2\"><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">challenges</font><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">, rewards</font><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">, fantasy</font><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">, immersion</font><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">, surprises</font><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">, control/dominance</font><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">, social interaction/bonding</font></font></li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"margin-left: 520px;\"><ul>\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\" size=\"+3\"><br>\nGuidelines:<br>\n</font>\n<ul>\n  <li><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\" size=\"+3\">Game <a href=\"game-story.htm\">story</a></font></li>\n  <li><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\" size=\"+3\">Game <a href=\"game-interface.htm\">interface</a></font></li>\n  <li><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\" size=\"+3\">Game <a href=\"game-mechanics.htm\">mechanics</a></font></li>\n  <li><font style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\" size=\"+3\">Game <a href=\"game-play.htm\">play</a></font></li>\n</ul>\n<font size=\"+3\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><br>\nNon-entertainment applications: education, training, following regimens</span><br style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">\n<br style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">\n</font><br>\n<br>\n\n\n</body></html>", "encoding": "ascii"}